{"id":"guide/developer-guide-overview","title":"Angular 开发者指南","contents":"<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"angular-developer-guides\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"70m4a29hup17ltm65vyv219c\">Angular 开发者指南<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/developer-guide-overview#angular-developer-guides\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"5bbvp3fm5fuak278iuad5xfm1\">作为一个应用程序框架，Angular 包含一系列集成良好的库，涵盖了各种特性。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"cu81dzfryj6av67rz73ybpum6\">Angular 库包括路由、表单管理、客户端-服务器通信等。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9k6ks01dhdzivfuywf4v3p3c7\">本主题列出了各种开发人员指南，供你了解有关这些 Angular 特性的更多信息，并帮助你在应用程序中正确使用每个特性。</p>\n<h2 id=\"prerequisites\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"e44b21uig1fakj5vcfuvz1bdu\">前提条件<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/developer-guide-overview#prerequisites\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8ihh39r3owciq2m2ntn0tmovp\">要充分利用这些开发人员指南，你应该查看以下主题：</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"94rl86q2f2b7rhc21ygp7pv27\"><a href=\"guide/what-is-angular\" title=\"What is Angular\\? | Angular\">什么是 Angular</a></li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"duipjg6v9boyuudh8vdct6z2m\"><a href=\"start\" title=\"Getting started with Angular | Angular\">入门教程</a></li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"mtmmhrywzez11px5heae3p87\"><a href=\"guide/understanding-angular-overview\" title=\"Understanding Angular | Angular\">了解 Angular</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"learn-about-angulars-features\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dpjygouyc32t1xu7d34msosom\">了解 Angular 的特性<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/developer-guide-overview#learn-about-angulars-features\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<div class=\"card-container\">\n  <a href=\"guide/routing-overview\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Routing and navigation developer guide\">\n    <section data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6ih4vj86fyrg1eqs17rhkyho3\">路由与导航</section>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"aowstde916wrnl2elhre2js26\">学习如何使用 Angular 路由器来处理页面导航和其它任务。</p>\n    <p class=\"card-footer\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9a9suvh0m7vdzxj5aomuljv0d\">路由器</p>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/forms-overview\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Angular forms developer guide\">\n    <section data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"5xsni8fgg13z9qwldwylke25i\">表单</section>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"c9ir706xbq8smv9m6znzeomv1\">学习 Angular 中做表单的两种方式：模板驱动表单和响应式表单。</p>\n    <p class=\"card-footer\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"5xsni8fgg13z9qwldwylke25i\">表单</p>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/understanding-communicating-with-http\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Angular HTTP client developer guide\">\n    <section>HTTP</section>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8pi3qpq48fxsj978uudj8nx1t\">学习如何在 Angular 中使用 HTTP 客户端服务来联系服务器。</p>\n    <p class=\"card-footer\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"f3ngk1xe34hm4po5jhxebu7xw\">HTTP 客户端</p>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/testing\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Angular testing developer guide\">\n    <section data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"etpgj6p39fywtmcrsphy8qrcg\">测试</section>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7ajv3lvnyvy1qw87uy6inedi4\">学习测试 Angular 应用的建议和技巧。</p>\n    <p class=\"card-footer\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"etpgj6p39fywtmcrsphy8qrcg\">测试</p>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/i18n-overview\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Angular internationalization developer guide\">\n    <section data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6o7gsxa0ot7g2f3jayrwusl09\">国际化</section>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"etz2q89lv6xcfioqee7d4wo2k\">学习如何本地化你的 Angular 应用。</p>\n    <p class=\"card-footer\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6q011lzpmyuok4ml6ed81l32n\">i18n 和 $localize</p>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/animations\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Angular animations developer guide\">\n    <section data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"918qr7iz61wsi82g2kwh1t9k\">动画片</section>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"bpyvzo0orv0iw7g5vx2kxsz5c\">学习如何为 Angular 应用添加动画。</p>\n    <p class=\"card-footer\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"918qr7iz61wsi82g2kwh1t9k\">动画片</p>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/service-worker-intro\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Angular service worker developer guide\">\n    <section data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8cxdv28bmkd2zv1q47jduilre\">Service Worker 与 PWA</section>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"c1yg6du924zbqrf8id1vc7anx\">学习如何使用 Service Worker 来创建渐进式 Web 应用（PWA）。</p>\n    <p class=\"card-footer\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8dp7xcvshs12idermzu6gife8\">Service worker 与 PWA</p>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/web-worker\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Web Workers\">\n    <section data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6fpkfht661ce0nbv7w5bi8064\">Web 工作线程</section>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"e8thwem4aw5pakpk2ioqorj0y\">学习如何使用 Web Worker 在后台线程中运行 CPU 密集型计算。</p>\n    <p class=\"card-footer\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6fpkfht661ce0nbv7w5bi8064\">Web 工作线程</p>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/ssr\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Server-side rendering\">\n    <section data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"63o3famemwo1dv6m2wf1liv55\">服务端渲染</section>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"70z641buo1iii3xf91oncct1c\">了解如何使用 Angular SSR 创建静态应用程序页面。</p>\n    <p class=\"card-footer\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"63o3famemwo1dv6m2wf1liv55\">服务端渲染</p>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/prerendering\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Pre-rendering\">\n    <section data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9zj9m1jufhgbnpydxvomydtt8\">预先渲染</section>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7sn9gsw0283428ltu2qna8ng2\">学习如何使用预先渲染在构建期间处理动态页面。</p>\n    <p class=\"card-footer\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9zj9m1jufhgbnpydxvomydtt8\">预先渲染</p>\n  </a>\n</div>\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最后复查时间：Fri Nov 05 2021</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - guide/what-is-angular\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - guide/animations\n - guide/developer-guide-overview#angular-developer-guides\n - guide/developer-guide-overview#learn-about-angulars-features\n - guide/developer-guide-overview#prerequisites\n - guide/forms-overview\n - guide/i18n-overview\n - guide/prerendering\n - guide/routing-overview\n - guide/service-worker-intro\n - guide/ssr\n - guide/testing\n - guide/understanding-angular-overview\n - guide/understanding-communicating-with-http\n - guide/web-worker\n - guide/what-is-angular\n - start\n-->"}